      1219,
      1184
    ],
    "category": "Formula",
    "text": "$$\nS_{ABCD} = 4^2 = 16, \\quad HB = \\frac{3}{4}AB = 3, \\quad \\tan 30^\\circ = \\frac{SH}{HB} \\Rightarrow SH = 3 \\cdot \\tan 30^\\circ = \\sqrt{3}.\n$$"
  },
  {
    "bbox": [
      252,
      1209,
      1089,
      1303
    ],
    "category": "Formula",
    "text": "$$\n\\text{Suy ra } V_{S.ABCD} = \\frac{1}{3} \\cdot \\sqrt{3} \\cdot 16 = \\frac{16\\sqrt{3}}{3} \\text{ mà } V_{S.ABC} = \\frac{1}{2}V_{S.ABCD} = \\frac{8\\sqrt{3}}{3}.\n$$"
  },
  {
    "bbox": [
      252,
