    "category": "Formula",
    "text": "$$\n\\Leftrightarrow \\frac{1}{(\\sqrt{3})^2} + \\frac{1}{4^2} = \\frac{1}{HN^2} \\Rightarrow HN = \\frac{4\\sqrt{57}}{19}.\n$$"
